                    <msContents>
                        <summary/>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <locus from="2r" to="12v"/>
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7051AmhCommChr">Amharic Commentary on Chronography</title>
                            <note>Presented with the title 'A short chronographical composition' and with the following incipit by 
                                <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/RSEA4WPK"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary"/><title level="m">Catalogue of Ethiopian Manuscripts in the British Library acquired since the Year 1877</title><author><forename>Stefan</forename><surname>Strelcyn</surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>British Museum</publisher><date>1978</date><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">British Museum</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1978BritishLibrary</note><citedRange unit="page">110</citedRange></bibl>. 
                                However, the incipit words <foreign xml:lang="am">ስማይንና፡ ምድርን፡ ፈጠረ፡</foreign> are more likely refer to works 
                                related to <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2314senafe">Śǝna fǝṭrat</ref> and suggest that it is more of a commentary 
                                that primarily discusses ethical or theological aspects.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="am"><foreign xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ንዌጥን፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ጽሒፈ፡ ዝንቱ፡
                                መጽሐፍ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡</foreign> ሰማይንና፡ ምድርን፡ ፈጠረ፡ በ፬ኛው፡ ቀን፡ ረቡዕ፡ በቀዳሚተ፡ ሰዓተ፡ ሌሊት፡ ጨርቃን፡ በምሥራቅ፡ ፀሐይን፡ በምዕራብ፡ በ፬ኛ፡ 
                                ሣልሲት፡ ከዋክብትን፡ በገጸ፡ ሰማይ፡ ለዘመን፡ መታወቂያ፡ ለሆኑ፡ ፈጠረ።</incipit>
                            <textLang xml:lang="am" otherLangs="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <locus from="12v" to="64v"/>
                            <title>Abbreviated Amharic version of the work of Abu Šākir</title>
                            <note>37 chapters of what is perhaps an Amharic translation or commentary of 
                                <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1011Abusak">ʾAbušākǝr</ref>.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="am"><foreign xml:lang="gez">ንግባዕኬ፡ ኀበ፡ ጥንተ፡ ነገር፡ ወንሕትታ፡ 
                                ለድ<supplied reason="undefined" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ን</supplied>ግል፡ ምሥጢር፤ አቡሻክር፡ ዘይቤ፡ አብ፡ ስብሐት፡ በዓለ፡ 
                                አኰቴት፡ ወልደ፡ አቢ፡ እልከረም፤ ዘይቤ፡ አበ፡ ምሕረት፡ በዓለ፡ ኂሩት፡ እብን፡ እልመአብ፡</foreign> ተተርጉፙል፡ ዘእሙር፡ በሪሽ፤ ዘ፡ ስመ፡ ሀገር፤ ቦክንፍ፤ አቡሻክር፡
                                በ<sic resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">፰</sic>፻ወ፮፻፶፡ ዓመተ፡ ዓለም፡ በ፲ወ፭፻፷ወ፱፡ ዓመተ፡ እስክንድር፡ በ፮፻፴ወ፭፡ ዓመተ፡ ተንባላት፡ ተነሥቷል፡ ይህንም፡ 
                                ዘመነ፡ ተንባላቱን፡ ወደ፡ ጨረቃ፡ ቢ<pb n="13r"/>መልሱት፡ ፮፻፶፭፡ ዘመን፡ ይሆናል፡ መየኀብር፡ ምስለ፡ ፮፻፶ወ፭ዓመት፡ ተንባላት፡ ያለው፡ ይህ፡ ነው። አንቀጽ፡ 
                                ፩ቦእምኔሆሙ፡ ዘገብሮ፡ በተፍጻሚተ፡ ዓመት፡ ወወሰከ፡ ማዕከለ፡ አውራኂሃ፡ ዘ፭ን፡ ጳጉሜ፡ በነሐሴና፡ በመስከረም፡ ማዕከል፡ ያገባ፡ አለ፡ ማለት፡ ነው፡</incipit>
                            <textLang xml:lang="am"/>
                        </msItem>
                    </msContents>
